      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "* \"It has never been easier to design your own silicon chip and now you can get 1,000 parts manufactured for just $7k USD.\"\n* \"It has never been easier to design your own silicon chip and now we will manufactured 1,000 parts for just $7k USD.\"\n * \"It has never been easier to design your own silicon chip and now wafer.space provides low cost manufacturing.\"",
